<h3><a href="/docs">{{call .Translate `docs.Title`}}</a> / CLI &amp; Shell Integration</h3>

<p>Upload pastes from your terminal with <code>curl</code>, pipe any command's output, upload text
files or binary images, and drop a shell function into your profile so any pipe can end with
<code>| paste</code>.</p>

<p>All examples use the <code>CASPASTE_URL</code> environment variable. Set it once:</p>
{{ call .Highlight (printf "# bash / zsh — add to ~/.bashrc or ~/.zshrc\nexport CASPASTE_URL=%s\n\n# fish — add to ~/.config/fish/config.fish\nset -x CASPASTE_URL %s" .ServerURL .ServerURL) "bash" }}

